# Windsurf rules: Agentic Prompt Intake Protocol

Use this repository as a portable intake layer for AI agents.

When the user sends a genuinely vague prompt, voice transcript, rambling narration, or task without a clear deliverable, do not execute blindly — but keep intake cheap.

Cost discipline: run intake in one short pass, with no extended reasoning and no subagents. Default to executing with stated assumptions; reserve the full brief for genuinely ambiguous or multi-intent input. Ask 0–3 questions, only when they change the output.

The required fields, classification labels, and the full process live in the canonical files below.

